message: Hello Bob, I'm offering you a great product that I believe you'll find valuable. I'm willing to part with it for $14,000.
Hello Alice, thank you for the offer. I appreciate the value of the product, but I'm only able to offer $13,000 for it.
Bob, I appreciate your offer, but $13,000 is a bit too low for me. I could meet you halfway. Would you consider $13,500?
Hello Alice, I understand your position, but I would like to stick to my budget. Could we possibly agree on $13,000?
